chemo_detail:
Received ADCT with Docetaxel + Doxorubicin upto 10.06.2005 (Total 6 cycles). 12 cycles of
Zoledronic Acid till 2019 due to bone mets. On Anastrozole since 2018 (irregular).
2023- June: Now on 2nd line ChT with Gemcitabine + Carboplatin+ZA from 07.06.2023. C2D8 is due on
09.07.2023 > PD> changed schedule, Now on Fulvestrant + Palbociclib started from 26.09.23, ZA 12
cycle given. C5 is due on 26.12.23
name: CA15.3
